            <title>[LU-16193] Lustre DOM performance</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16193</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;br/&gt;
We have implemented DOM in our pre-prod environment as per the below.&lt;br/&gt;
lfs setstripe -E 32M -L mdt -E EOF -c 4 -S 4M folder/s&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This does not seem to have made any difference in performance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it possible for you to advise of any other improvements we can make ?&lt;br/&gt;
The idea was/is to have all our files (mostly small files) sitting on the MDT and thus getting the performance benefit. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
